title: Petra Flannery
itunes:title: Petra Flannery
description: One of the most sought-after celebrity stylists, Petra Flannery has built an enormous career out of following her instincts when it comes to fashion. In this episode, Petra highlights the elegance of simplicity, and shares how we can find timeless inspiration in others - and tap into our OWN personal style.
